#

Shrimp Avocado Salad

20 min
$15
320 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePaleoLow-Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuick

Description

A refreshing and light salad featuring succulent shrimp and creamy avocado, perfect for a healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • avocado: 2 ripe
  • mixed greens (such as arugula and spinach): 4 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1 medium
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
